YoDC
YoDC will be comprising of two programs (peer side and hub side). Peer will have nick name and some share files and folders. These files and folders are stored in the tree form as an object of an class. Peer will connect to hub and send its shared files to hub. Hub in return will send the information of all the online users. Peer can then browse file list of any online user and can download file or folder from their file list. Peer can also query for any file from hub and hub will reply with the file list allowing peer to download file or directory. There will also be the feature of common messaging where peers can collectively communicate. 
